      "updated": 1774106271
    },
    {
      "id": "67f4ef4f00000000007d5066",
      "text": "[CJK統合漢字]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744105295,
      "updated": 1744105298
    },
    {
      "id": "69beb720000000000010c6a9",
      "text": "漢字が使われている３カ国語の頭文字を取ってCJKと命名されている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774106400,
      "updated": 1774106418
    },
    {
      "id": "69beb6a6000000000010c6a8",
      "text": "\t[中国語]（Chinese）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774106279,
      "updated": 1774106421
    },
    {
      "id": "69beb734000000000010c6aa",
      "text": "\t[日本語]（Japanese）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774106421,
      "updated": 1774106428
    },
    {
      "id": "69beb73b000000000010c6ab",
      "text": "\t[韓国語]・[朝鮮語]（Korean）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774106428,
      "updated": 1774106428
    },
    {
      "id": "69beb766000000000010c6ac",
      "text": "これに[ベトナム語]・[越語]（Vietnamese）も含めると[CJKV]となる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774106470,
      "updated": 1774106548
    },
    {
